[DQR.IFRS.0105.9556] The following elements are in the presentation linkbase of 06 - Estado de flujos de efectivo [resumen] but are not included in any calculation relationship in the filing. ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForFinanceIncome, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForGainsLossesOnFairValueAdjustmentInvestmentProperty, ifrs-full:OtherAdjustmentsForWhichCashEffectsAreInvestingOrFinancingCashFlow, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForUndistributedProfitsOfInvestmentsAccountedForUsingEquityMethod, ifrs-full:ProfitLossBeforeTax, realiabusiness:VariacionDeProvisionesYOtrasCorreccionesValorativasPorDeterioro, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForFinanceCosts, ifrs-full:PaymentsToAcquireOrRedeemEntitysShares All elements appearing in the face of the financial statements should be included in a calculation relationship somewhere in the filing.
